#

Pan-Seared New York Strip Steak with Red Wine Reduction

$25
600 kcal

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

PaleoGluten-Free

Tags:

SteakMain CourseHigh-ProteinGourmet

Description

A succulent pan-seared New York strip steak topped with a rich red wine reduction, perfect for a gourmet experience.

Ingredients

  • New York Strip Steak: 1 lb
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Olive Oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Shallots: 2, minced
  • Red Wine: 1 cup
  • Beef Broth: 1/2 cup
  • Butter: 2 tablespoons
  • Fresh Thyme: 1 teaspoon, chopped
